## Profiling

### CPU Profiling

```go
import (
    "os"
    "runtime/pprof"
)

func main() {
    // Start CPU profiling
    f, err := os.Create("cpu.prof")
    if err != nil {
        log.Fatal(err)
    }
    defer f.Close()

    if err := pprof.StartCPUProfile(f); err != nil {
        log.Fatal(err)
    }
    defer pprof.StopCPUProfile()

    // Your code here
    runApplication()
}

// Analyze:
